# Environment Variables for IHM Marine Services

# Resend API Key
# Get your API key from: https://resend.com/api-keys
RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Sign up at https://resend.com (free tier: 3,000 emails/month)
# 2. Get your API key from the dashboard
# 3. Create a .env.local file (copy this template)
# 4. Replace 'your_resend_api_key_here' with your actual API key
# 5. Add .env.local to .gitignore (already done in most Vite projects)
#
# For Vercel deployment:
# - Add RESEND_API_KEY to your Vercel project environment variables
# - Settings > Environment Variables > Add New
